{"word":"G4599 - σθενόω - sthenóō - sthen-o'-o - Strengthen","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σθενόω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">sthenóō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">sthen-o'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Strengthen</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பலப்படுத்து"},{"paragraph":"to make strong, to strengthen"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <b>&#x03C3;&#x03B8;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03BD;&#x03BF;&#x03C2;</b> <b>sthenos</b> (bodily <i>vigor</i>; probably akin to the base of <a href=\"#/G2476 - ἵστημι - hístēmi - his'-tay-mee/2476\">G2476</a>); to <i>strengthen</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>confirm</i> (in spiritual knowledge and power): - strengthen.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}